Anyway, right, I see who said it.

126
00:13:37,601 --> 00:13:44,320
Okay, so we're always, we're going to always find that there is a third possibility, the Russian Orthodox.

127
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,560
But it's hard to see, that's what I want to tell you.

