00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:18,361
So, what he says is, Jesus didn't perform miracles to get people to believe in God.

150
00:16:18,361 --> 00:16:20,361
That's what the Grand Inquisitor says.

151
00:16:20,361 --> 00:16:23,160
